                                    <cell>Cash on hand, Postal Savings Bank this day</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">29,381.15</cell>
                                </row>
                            </table>
                            <p rend="center"><hi rend="italic">Expenses Provisional Government
                                    memorandum</hi>.</p>
                            <table cols="2" rows="1">
                                <row>
                                    <cell>Expenses Provisional Government this date</cell>
                                    <cell role="num">$159,954.21</cell>
                                </row>
                            </table>
                            <p>This amount covers all expenses, including military and items not
                                appropriated by the last legislature.</p>
                            <p rend="center"><hi rend="italic">Memorandum cash in treasury
                                    outstanding</hi>.</p>
                            <table cols="2" rows="10">
